title: Seidio CAPSA Touchview Case with Metal Kickstand and Holster Combo for Apple iPhone 6 - Retail Packaging - Black
features: Seamless bond between screen protector and rim keeps your device guarded from dust and debris
Oleophobic coating helps prevent the appearance of fingerprint smudges on screen
Exceeds the MIL-STD-810G standard and can survive drops from up to 4 feet

description: Seidio's CAPSA TouchView Case with Metal Kickstand Combo contains a CAPSA with Metal Kickstand case and CAPSA holster. The CAPSA TouchView with Metal Kickstand case has an innovative design that provides all-around protection for your Apple iPhone 6. The integrated screen protector easily snaps onto the case, safeguarding your screen from scratches and eliminating the hassle of installing separate screen protectors. The CAPSA Holster features a removable belt-clip, optional locking mechanism and can hold your Apple iPhone 6 face-in or face-out. Use them together when you're on-the-go and worry more about moving forward and less about your device.
